node.text:
I had so much fun partnering with @marshalls to turn something one shopper found in the store (#ad) into the ultimate WOW cooking experience. I helped Liz put her kitchen find to good use during a virtual cooking class where we made homemade pasta! Marshalls is turning awesome finds fans share on social into big WOWs IRL.  @e_batch5 @sweetnizcakeshop 

Share your favorite finds with #MarshallsWOW and #contest, and Marshalls could WOW you next! 

No purchase because. 50 U.S.  DC, Par, 18+. Rules & entry deadlines: Marshallswow.dja.com

node.text: This marinated cherry tomato pasta is everything I love about summer food... hardly any cooking, fresh ingredients & tons of flavor! Cherry tomatoes marinate w/ olive oil, lemon, shallots, garlic & pepper flakes for a few hours to marry the flavors, then toss w/ fresh basil, parm and your fav pasta! recipe on @thegiadzy
